Explosion Kills Eight in Nigerian City of Maiduguri, Nation Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-07-25T08:30:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/explosion-kills-eight-in-nigerian-city-of-maiduguri-nation-says.html
A blast in the city of Maiduguri in
the northeast of  Nigeria  killed eight people yesterday,  The
Nation  newspaper reported, citing an eyewitness, Badiga Bukar.  A military spokesman in the region, Lieutenant-Colonel
Hassan Mohammed, refused to confirm the casualty figure, the
Lagos-based newspaper said. Three soldiers were injured in the
attack, he was cited as saying.  The Islamic sect Boko Haram, which draws its inspiration
from  Afghanistan â€™s Taliban movement, has been accused of a
series of attacks in Maiduguri.  To contact the reporter on this story:
